			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Brilliant site, Graham, an absolute mine of information. Having lived and worked in Vienna and Mons over the final 13 years before my retirement at the end of 2013 I have visited many of these sites, the ones in Bohemia multiple times. I cannot recommend them too highly &#8211; well preserved, good beer, hearty cuisine, friendly people, beautiful countryside and towns. What’s not to like!</p>
