					<description><![CDATA[Dear Graham,
If you need to investigate more deeply on general Nicolas Philippe GUYE , Napoleon&#039;s officer, I can give some keys.
I&#039;m not descendant of Nicolas Philippe but from one of his brothers.
Nicolas had one son , Pierre Adolphe Janey-Guye  , from extra conjugal relation , dead 23 years old , not married , and two girls Hermine and Clélie born 1816.12.30 and 1819.01.31 at Saint Dié  .]]></description>
			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Dear Graham,<br />
If you need to investigate more deeply on general Nicolas Philippe GUYE , Napoleon&#8217;s officer, I can give some keys.<br />
I&#8217;m not descendant of Nicolas Philippe but from one of his brothers.<br />
Nicolas had one son , Pierre Adolphe Janey-Guye  , from extra conjugal relation , dead 23 years old , not married , and two girls Hermine and Clélie born 1816.12.30 and 1819.01.31 at Saint Dié  .</p>
]]></content:encoded>
		
